Acquisitions
We are currently acquiring homes through single asset purchases, new construction with homebuilders and stabilized portfolios of occupied homes. We are actively buying in Charlotte, Raleigh, Nashville, Phoenix, Denver and Colorado Springs. We also consider portfolios or new construction opportunities in the additional markets where we operate.
Our general minimum buying criteria is as follows:

3+ bedrooms
2+ bathrooms
1,000+ sq ft
1980+ vintage
$1,100+ rent rates (depending on the individual market)
Good school ratings & low crime areas

For submissions or questions about acquisition opportunities, please contact:
Blake Keathley
480-800-3331
[email protected]


Dispositions
We have an active pipeline of disposition properties throughout our portfolio. For questions or information on homes that are actively marketed, please contact:
Andrew Mellor
480-800-3427
[email protected]
 
 
