colony starwood homes
Public Company









Company Profile
Sector: Financials
Industry: Real Estate
Sub-Industry: REIT
Colony Starwood Homes operates as a real estate investment trust. The Company acquires, renovates, leases and manages residential assets including single-family rental homes and distressed and non-performing residential mortgage loans.




