New Homes in Celina, TX



















































Skip to content

















                    Celina New Homes
                


Celina, Texas is a peaceful city located 30 miles north of Dallas. Nestled in the gently-rolling hills of Collin and Denton counties, this city offers excellent services and proximity to Dallas' numerous amenities. While the city has experienced notable economic growth in the past few years, residents are able to live a peaceful life here. Celina draws in many new residents with its outstanding schools, wonderful parks, and diverse shopping options, not to mentions all the great new homes for sale in Dallas. The city is served by the Celina Independent School District which is known for excellent schools. Public schools in the area provide the young ones with outstanding education and extracurricular activities. The Celina High School football team is one of the most successful in Texas, with a 68-game winning streak! Individuals who wish to pursue a university degree can attend the nearby University of North Texas or the University of Texas at Dallas. Those keen on reading and furthering their research will love the Celina Public Library! Downtown Celina is a lively place which boasts excellent stores and restaurants. The Historic Square is a pedestrian-friendly area and the spot where many community events take place. Residents can also visit nearby shopping malls, such as the Prestonbrook Crossing. The Village at Fairview is a large mall located nearby offering over 150 stores, many restaurants, and numerous entertainment options! The city features three excellent parks. Old Celina Park is Celina's crown jewel and includes an award-winning baseball complex, soccer fields, a pavilion, a playground and a fishing pond - perfect for family gatherings! Residents can also easily reach the Ray Roberts Lake State Park, a wonderful natural oasis where one can enjoy swimming, boating, picnicking, and kayaking. Celina is one of those rare places that still has that unique small-town charm to it. With excellent amenities, notable schools and great shopping opportunities, Celina is the perfect place for living. Regardless of your age, occupation, and interests, this warm community will make you feel at home in this city. Residents who wish to relocate to this city can refer to New Home Source in order to find great offers in Celina. The comprehensive listings of New Home Source will help home buyers find their perfect home in no time. And even if you can't find your perfect match in Celina, our site can help you expand your search and find new homes in Frisco or McKinney or even search all the new real estate in Dallas. 














