Corporate Profile
















Webcast 
            Second Quarter 2017 Earnings Conference Call
            Thursday, August 10th, 2017
            11:00 AM ET
            Domestic: 1-877-407-9039 
            International: 1-201-689-8470 








On January 5, 2016, Starwood Waypoint Residential Trust completed its merger with Colony American Homes, Inc.  In connection with the merger, the name of the Company was changed to Colony Starwood Homes. On January 6, 2016, the Company’s common shares began trading under the ticker symbol "SFR" on the New York Stock Exchange. 
Colony Starwood Homes acquires, renovates, leases, maintains and manages single family homes. Colony Starwood Homes is Reinventing Renting™ by building a leading, nationally recognized brand that is based on a foundation of respect for its residents and the communities in which it operates.

 



